### Prompt Generation Rules
- Keep prompts atomic and focused
- Include TDD instructions
- Reference specific files, not entire directories
- Limit context to essential information

## Anti-Patterns to Avoid
- ‚ùå Generic `any` types
- ‚ùå Console.log in production code
- ‚ùå Synchronous file operations
- ‚ùå Direct file system access in providers
- ‚ùå Date objects in API responses (use strings)
- ‚ùå Complex nested promises (use async/await)
- ‚ùå cd commands in terminal (already in workspace)
- ‚ùå Importing from individual files instead of barrel exports
- ‚ùå Importing from non-existent paths (e.g., './task-management/types')
- ‚ùå Using relative paths that dont match actual directory structure

